data.description: Stunning custom built Twilight Home located in the Heart of the North Valley in the gated Lavender Fields community. Home features 2,926sf with 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, a loft and private pool! Spacious main living area with wood look tile floors and a gas fireplace with stone accents. Chefs kitchen with upgraded cabinetry, granite countertops, backsplash, black stainless built-in oven/microwave, range, rangehood, fridge, center island and more. Separate dining space. 1st floor owner's suite with a spa like bath. Bath hosts his/hers sinks, a free standing soaker tub, walk-in shower with custom tile work and walk-in closet! Upstairs loft perfect for a 2nd living area. 2nd master located upstairs with a private bath! Great yard fully walled with a huge heated pool with automatic cover
